Package: Pareto
Type: Package
Title: A tool kit for the Pareto and the piecewise Pareto distribution 
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ulrich", "Riegel", email = "ulrich.riegel@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utilities for the Pareto and piecewise Pareto distribution
    that are useful for reinsurance pricing. In particular, the package provides
    a non-trivial algorithm that can be used to match the expected losses of a 
    tower of reinsurance layers with a layer-independent collective risk model.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Suggests: 
    testthat, knitr, rmarkdown
URL: https://github.com/ulrichriegel/Pareto#pareto
Language: en-US
